.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-EXPORT-JSON" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-export-json \- export wallet ledger as JSON
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-export-json
.RI [ wallet ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Dumps the entire
.B ledger
table from the wallet database as a JSON object containing
.B wallet
name and a
.B ledger
array.
Returns
.B {"ok":false}
if the database does not exist.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"wallet":..., "ledger":[...]}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-export-csv (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-transaction-log (1)
